{"id":2,"date":"2025-03-19T23:56:03","date_gmt":"2025-03-19T23:56:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.puppetemporium.com\/?page_id=2"},"modified":"2025-10-29T19:01:43","modified_gmt":"2025-10-29T19:01:43","slug":"sample-page","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/temp.puppetemporium.com\/?page_id=2","title":{"rendered":"About Us"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p><strong>Rare. Unusual. Always One-of-a-Kind.<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Welcome to Puppet Emporium, the premier destination for rare, vintage, and highly collectible puppets, dolls, and ventriloquist dummies. Many with fascinating histories.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Our collection features handcrafted marionettes, antique dolls, and ventriloquist dummies that have been luckily acquired or mysteriously found. Whether you&#8217;re a serious collector, a curious enthusiast, or simply looking for a unique conversation piece, we have something for you. Browse our collection today before it&#8217;s gone.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Our Philosophy<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>At Puppet Emporium, we believe every puppet has a story to tell. We carefully source, restore, and rehome puppets and dolls from private collections, estate sales, and other locations we\u2019d rather not disclose.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>We don\u2019t ask too many questions, and neither should you.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h3 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Our Founder<\/strong><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Puppet Emporium was founded by Edwin P. Wetherby, a lifelong collector and puppeteer. His fascination with rare puppets and dolls began at an early age when he inherited a mysterious marionette from a distant relative. What started as a small collection quickly grew into an obsession, leading Edwin to travel the world in search of forgotten treasures. He acquires pieces from estate sales, antique shops, and sources best left unnamed.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>With an uncanny ability to find rare collectibles, Edwin established Puppet Emporium to share his discoveries with those who appreciate the artistry and craftsmanship of these unique figures. Today, his hand-selected inventory continues to intrigue and delight collectors worldwide.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Rare. Unusual. Always One-of-a-Kind. Welcome to Puppet Emporium, the premier destination for rare, vintage, and highly collectible puppets, dolls, and [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"open","template":"","meta":{"site-sidebar-layout":"default","site-content-layout":"","ast-site-content-layout":"default","site-content-style":"default","site-sidebar-style":"default","ast-global-header-display":"","ast-banner-title-visibility":"","ast-main-header-display":"","ast-hfb-above-header-display":"","ast-hfb-below-header-display":"","ast-hfb-mobile-header-display":"","site-post-title":"","ast-breadcrumbs-content":"","ast-featured-img":"","footer-sml-layout":"","ast-disable-related-posts":"","theme-transparent-header-meta":"","adv-header-id-meta":"","stick-header-meta":"","header-above-stick-meta":"","header-main-stick-meta":"","header-below-stick-meta":"","astra-migrate-meta-layouts":"default","ast-page-background-enabled":"default","ast-page-background-meta":{"desktop":{"background-color":"var(--ast-global-color-5)","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""},"tablet":{"background-color":"","background-image":"","background-repeat":"repeat","background-position":"center center","background-size":"auto","background-attachment":"scroll","background-type":"","background-media":"","overlay-type":"","overlay-color":"","overlay-opacity":"","overlay-gradient":""},"mobile":{"background-color":"","background-image":"","background-repe